---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Gist — Turn your app idea into a build-ready spec">
  <header class="site-header animate-in">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="logo" aria-label="Gist home"
        ><svg class="logo-mark" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"
          ><defs
            ><linearGradient id="logo-g" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"
              ><stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--color-logo-from)"></stop><stop
                offset="100%"
                stop-color="var(--color-logo-to)"></stop></linearGradient
            ></defs
          ><rect width="32" height="32" rx="8" fill="url(#logo-g)"></rect><text
            x="50%"
            y="53%"
            dominant-baseline="central"
            text-anchor="middle"
            font-family="Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif"
            font-size="20"
            font-style="italic"
            fill="var(--color-logo-fg)">G</text
          ></svg
        ><span class="logo-text">Gist</span></a
      >
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow animate-in">Zero-stack app specifications</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title animate-in-delay-1">
          Describe your idea.<br />
          <em class="hero-accent">Get a spec AI can build from.</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle animate-in-delay-2">
          Answer a few questions about your app &mdash; what it does, who it's for, where the data
          lives. Gist turns your answers into a deployment-ready specification that any AI coding
          assistant can implement without the back-and-forth.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions animate-in-delay-3">
          <a href="/create" class="btn btn-primary btn-hero"
            >Create your spec <span class="btn-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a
          >
          <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true" />

    <section id="how-it-works" class="steps">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to a build-ready spec</h2>
        <ol class="step-list">
          <li class="step">
            <span class="step-number">1</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Describe your idea</h3>
              <p>Title, one-line description, and what your users see first. No jargon required.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <span class="step-number">2</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Answer a few questions</h3>
              <p>
                We ask about data, hosting, and design. Every option is laid out with trade-offs
                visible &mdash; pick what fits, skip what doesn't matter.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <span class="step-number">3</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Download your spec</h3>
              <p>
                A markdown file with architecture decisions, security guidance, implementation
                order, and a suggested prompt for your AI assistant.
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="spec-preview-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What you get</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          A real spec &mdash; not a template. Tailored to your answers, right-sized to your app's
          complexity.
        </p>
        <div class="spec-preview">
          <div class="spec-preview-header">
            <div class="spec-preview-dots">
              <span class="spec-preview-dot dot-red"></span>
              <span class="spec-preview-dot dot-yellow"></span>
              <span class="spec-preview-dot dot-green"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="spec-preview-filename">weather-now-gist-spec-v1.0.md</span>
          </div>
          <pre
            class="spec-preview-body"><code># Weather Now &mdash; Gist Specification

## Meta
- Gist version: 1.0
- Complexity tier: minimal

## Summary
&gt; A clutter-free personal weather app. Fetches weather
&gt; from Open-Meteo (free, no key) directly from the
&gt; browser. Plain HTML/CSS/JS &mdash; no framework, no build
&gt; step, no server. Deploy static files to Cloudflare Pages.

## Architecture
- Host: Cloudflare Pages (free tier)
- Framework: None &mdash; plain HTML/CSS/JS
- Proxy: None (API is free, no key needed)

## Implementation Order
1. Scaffold: index.html, style.css, app.js, favicon
2. HTML shell with loading/error/success states
3. Styles: cool palette, dark mode, responsive
4. Connect: Open-Meteo API + Nominatim geocoding
5. Web standards: og:image, CSP, meta tags
6. Deploy: push to Cloudflare Pages

## Suggested Prompt
"Build step by step, starting with mock data..."</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="value-props">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why a spec matters</h2>
        <div class="value-grid">
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"
                ><path
                  d="M3 10h14M10 3v14"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3>Right-sized architecture</h3>
            <p>
              A simple app gets 4 static files. A complex one gets Workers, KV, and cron. Your spec
              matches your actual needs.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"
                ><rect
                  x="3"
                  y="8"
                  width="14"
                  height="9"
                  rx="2"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"></rect><path
                  d="M6 8V5a4 4 0 118 0v3"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3>Security from the start</h3>
            <p>
              API keys never touch your frontend. Trust boundaries are explicit. The pre-ship
              checklist catches what you'd miss.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"
                ><path
                  d="M4 16l4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4l4 4m-4-4L4 8"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path
                  d="M14 6h2m0 0v2m0-2l-3 3"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3>Less back-and-forth</h3>
            <p>
              Without a spec, your AI assistant asks a dozen clarifying questions. With one, it can
              start building immediately.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"
                ><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
                ></circle><path
                  d="M10 6v4l2.5 2.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg
              >
            </div>
            <h3>Free tier aware</h3>
            <p>
              Every recommendation fits within free tier limits. Budget math is included &mdash; no
              surprise charges.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="cta-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to build something?</h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">
          Five minutes of questions. A spec you can hand to any AI coding assistant.
        </p>
        <a href="/create" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          >Create your spec <span class="btn-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a
        >
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>
        Built with Gist. Open source on <a
          href="https://github.com/1mb-dev/gistapp"
          class="footer-link">GitHub</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>

<style>
  /* header — extends global .site-header */
  .site-header {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  /* hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-20);
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 680px;
    height: 480px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, var(--color-accent-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    filter: blur(40px);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-normal);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .hero-accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* button size variants (extends global .btn) */
  .btn-hero {
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .btn-lg {
    padding: 0.875rem 2.25rem;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .btn-arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform var(--duration-fast) var(--easing);
  }

  .btn:hover .btn-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  /* steps */
  .steps {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-20);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-normal);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--space-8));
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .step-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  /* spec preview */
  .spec-preview-section {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-20);
  }

  .spec-preview {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .spec-preview-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
    background: var(--color-bg-sunken);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .spec-preview-dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .spec-preview-dot {
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  }

  .dot-red {
    background: #e5534b;
    opacity: 0.65;
  }
  .dot-yellow {
    background: #d4a72c;
    opacity: 0.65;
  }
  .dot-green {
    background: #3fb950;
    opacity: 0.65;
  }

  .spec-preview-filename {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .spec-preview-body {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: none;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .spec-preview-body code {
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: inherit;
  }

  /* value props */
  .value-props {
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-sunken);
  }

  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition:
      border-color var(--duration-normal) var(--easing),
      box-shadow var(--duration-normal) var(--easing),
      transform var(--duration-normal) var(--easing);
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-subtle);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-accent-subtle);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-glow {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 500px;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, var(--color-accent-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
    filter: blur(30px);
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-normal);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
  }

  .cta-subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* footer */
  .site-footer {
    padding: var(--space-10) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .footer-link {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition:
      color var(--duration-fast) var(--easing),
      text-decoration-color var(--duration-fast) var(--easing);
    padding-block: var(--space-2);
    min-height: 44px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* responsive */
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
